Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:09.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,Dati otkaz
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala vam na svemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:12.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,Otarasi se stvari
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve ukupno će biti oko 30.000.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:17.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Banka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:18.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Išida Šoja
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve podižem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,Vraćam ti novac
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,Poslednji dan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:33.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs100}Oblik glasa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,Odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedite na svoja mesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Od danas imate novu drugaricu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta 'oćeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Imaš sreće, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Devojčica je.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš me briga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirni?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro, možeš da se predstaviš.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je. Ja sam Nišimija Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:13.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nadam se da ću moći da se sprijateljim sa vama uz pomoć ove sveske.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:17.54,Signs,,0,0,0,,Slobodno je koristite kada želite da pričate sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:32.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ja sam gluva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pozdrav, Nišimija. Ja sam Kavai Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto, drago mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, umeš li ti da pričaš japanski?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao, kakva si.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Možeš li da ponoviš?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Imaš li neki nadimak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Odustajem! Predajem se!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo, je li?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isti kao Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaže da joj je nadimak Šo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš fino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Baš nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro, zapišite sledeće odeljke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Od strane 20 do strane 25, i vežbajte probleme sa strane 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To će biti na sledećem kontrolnom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj mi tvoju svesku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Prva je tačka oslonca. Kako joj ime kaže, oslonac je za polugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zatim je tu sila primenjena na jednu stranu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I na kraju teret koji se podiže ili spušta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zavisno od lokacije, postoje tri vrste poluga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, poranila si.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću ti reći kada da počneš, u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo ponovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ćemo ovako ići na takmičenje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemamo šanse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo ti je kazna za to što si jadan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć, boli.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Boli!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Znate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet nisam mogla da se skoncentrišem pola časa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kopiraću ti moje beleške posle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ja nisam ništa zgrešio.\NZato se nikada neću izviniti—"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Na šta to liči, Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboravi. Dalje.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cvikeraš jedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Počinješ odavde.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pvekini viže da budež tvdogvav,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,vekva je majka, uždahnuži.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Neču da še ižvinim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sledeći, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mora da me zezaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne zavitlavaj se, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Možete li da mi kažete o čemu ste pričale?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo nazad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ćao, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš šta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne budeš pažljivija, zamrzeće te svi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pvijatelji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Odvratna si!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam Kita iz udruženja gluvih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li ste čuli za znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To je jezik gde pričate rukama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Možete da vodite čitave razgovore koristeći samo ruke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije divno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.15,Alt,,0,0,0,,Znakovni jezik...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I šta kažete na ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Da biste mogli više da pričate sa Šoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,da li biste hteli da posvetite tri minuta dnevno učenju znakovnog jezika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nastavnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije dovoljno da pišemo u njenu svesku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo bi lakše za Šoko ako bi mogla da koristi znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali meni je lakše da pišem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću naučiti znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pokaži mi "Sahara Mijoko" znakovnim jezikom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sa."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulizice jedna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Obožavam ga. Tako je kul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A, biće u seriji sledeće nedelje. Ne smem to da propustim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar joj odeća nije baš jadna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj naglas, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovom knjigom je autor hteo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i nakon eksperimenta, mangan dioksid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirose, ti uzmi tu stranu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nišimija..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I zvezdica.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, preteruješ, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš? Ja mislim da je ovo taman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji si zloća.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Koga briga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro izgleda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:22.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Svaka čast, Nišimija! Sahara je otišla negde.\NNauči nas da govorimo nišimijanskim! Jej! Jej!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,U, joj, ko li je ovo uradio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako zlobno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću obrisati ovo za tebe, u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve čisto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema na čemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokom perioda Đomon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, bre, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Usred časa smo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, izvinjavam se!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde smo sad stali...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, u kakvim su kućama živeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadila si se, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li zapravo možeš da čuješ kada nosiš ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno, to sam se i ja pitala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokaži mi ih na trenutak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj da vidim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Odvratno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(60,38.925)}Jesi li rekla nešto?\NGlupačo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1860,38.925)}Kakve mišiće imam!\NMišić-mija Šoko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta da radimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Preterao si, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Zbornica
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taj cvikeraš me baš nervira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je? Pomeri se.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Smetaš nam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ona to radi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta lupetaš? Ako imaš neki problem, reci tako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti me! Odvratna si!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, Nišimija je zanimljiva.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoja je skroz pocrveneo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ona to radi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Skroz je opičena.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se, Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Postoji nešto o čemu moramo da popričamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,U pitanju je Nišimija Šoko, koja je odsutna danas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Njena majka nas je kontaktirala juče.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Osam njenih slušnih aparata su nestali ili pokvareni u proteklih pet meseci.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Njena majka veruje da je maltretiraju u školi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li je iko od vas primetio da neko maltretira ili se loše ponaša prema Nišimiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Čini se da su slušni aparati jako skupi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas da ne pravite više problema svojim roditeljima...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To si bio ti, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ustani više!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti si sedela pored njega, šta kažeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguće da je zadirkivao pomalo, sa vremena na vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A ti, Šimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, ja sam mu rekao da prestane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali on me nije slušao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Šimada, i ti si kriv koliko i ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A i devojčice su je stalno ogovarale iza leđa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pogotovo Ueno i Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja to nikada ne bih uradila!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si takav?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, užasan si!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasplakao ju je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore\NNišimija Šoko, odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Otkud ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:18.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(60,38.925)}O čemu ste pričale?\NSkapiraj sama.\NIzvinite.\NOtišle smo jer si spora!\NGlupačo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:18.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1860,38.925)}Šta nam treba za sutra?\NKompas.\NHvala ti.\NŠta je učitelj rekao?\NNe znam, ne čujem. <3\NIzvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se zbog svega.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, naravno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doviđenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stani, Šoja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoj učitelj mi je sve ispričao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, zašto si tako mokar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosadna si. Skočio sam sa mosta kao i uvek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stani!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li pravio probleme drugima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da me smaraš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li istina to što je tvoj učitelj rekao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, istina je!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo kod Nišimije.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Spremi se.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,Banka Mizuho
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo kući, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Od sutra budi dobar dečak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Zvali su ih "došljacima", i imali su mnoge probleme.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, šta to radiš sa mojim stolom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta si to radila, gadiš mi se!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet taj izraz lica.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini da izigravaš dobricu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je? Ako želiš nešto da kažeš, reci to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne razumem taj tvoj glupav izraz lica,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,i nerviraš me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, reci više!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si to uradila?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tobom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudim še...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudim še naibole što mogu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to govoriš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je, bre?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne razumem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:26.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,Gubi se, Išida.\NKada ćeš više da nestaneš?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno me nervira...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija je promenila školu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To je to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, ko je bio redar juče?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam dobio spisak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I ko je bio zadužen za cveće?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:13.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,Časovi znakovnog jezika
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Šoko, zdravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sećaš li me se?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz šestog razreda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.87,0:24:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.08,0:24:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.34,0:24:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.23,0:24:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.32,0:24:33.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore\NNišimija Šoko, odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Došao sam ovo da ti vratim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.66,0:24:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgubila si je.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.39,0:24:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto znam znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Naučio sam ga.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.85,0:24:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,U svakom slučaju, evo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.42,0:24:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada možda ne želiš da je vidiš.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.85,0:25:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.67,0:25:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja i ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li bismo mogli da budemo prijatelji?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.16,0:25:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to ja govorim?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.24,0:25:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, pa ona je isto govorila onda u osnovnoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.69,0:25:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Konačno sam shvatio.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.87,0:25:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da plačeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.40,0:25:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da plačeš, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.94,0:25:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li bismo mogli da budemo prijatelji?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.72,0:25:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.50,0:25:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.70,0:25:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.18,0:25:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Probudi se!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.63,0:25:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Vreme je za doručak!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.28,0:26:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Probudi se, Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.95,0:26:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro, Marija.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.86,0:26:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo je ustao!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.47,0:26:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Odoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.23,0:26:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ćao, mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.65,0:26:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Srećno danas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.66,0:26:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.07,0:26:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatno.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.09,0:26:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jedi koliko voliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.88,0:26:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto se tako smeškaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.44,0:26:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, znaš...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.83,0:26:55.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Vraćam ti novac
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.47,0:26:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Puno si radio za ovo, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.04,0:27:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak si prodao i svoje mange, odeću i dušek.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.75,0:27:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali srećna sam što si bio spreman toliko da učiniš.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.63,0:27:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, Šo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.40,0:27:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si poželeo da se ubiješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.91,0:27:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pa, svašta se izdešavalo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.28,0:27:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali znaš, više...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.23,0:27:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako sam i mislila.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.33,0:27:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači bila sam u pravu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.70,0:27:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Znala sam da nešto ne valja!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.94,0:27:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja soba je bila previše čista!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.72,0:27:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam mogla da te dobijem na telefon!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.83,0:27:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I kakav je ono zlokoban kalendar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.25,0:27:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve stranice nakon aprila su bile istrgnute...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako mi ne obećaš da ćeš odustati od toga, spaliću sve.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.18,0:27:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Spaliću 1,7 miliona jena koje si svojim znojem zaradio!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.06,0:27:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej! Slušaš li me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.60,0:27:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.73,0:27:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.03,0:27:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta {\i1}ti{\i0} radiš, nesrećni sine moj!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.15,0:28:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček... Izvini!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.84,0:28:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Istinski se izvinjavam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.24,0:28:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću to uraditi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.22,0:28:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću to uraditi! Izvini! Stvarno!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.93,0:28:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta nećeš uraditi! Lepo mi reci!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.62,0:28:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću se ubiti!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.56,0:28:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću pokušati da se ubijem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.32,0:28:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.20,0:28:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.15,0:28:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.42,0:28:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Obećao si, u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.78,0:28:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.86,0:28:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.98,0:28:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Vodu!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Juče sam planirao da skočim sa visokog mosta i umrem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.85,0:28:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To što sam otišao da vidim Nišimiju je bila samo priprema.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.37,0:28:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bio je to najveći test hrabrosti mog života.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.18,0:28:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.29,0:29:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.98,0:29:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta sam to učinio?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.02,0:29:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokom ceremonije upisa u nižu srednju, čuo sam Šimadu...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.74,0:29:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bolje se ne približavaj liku po imenu Išida Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.37,0:29:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On je maltretirao ljude.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.71,0:29:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shvatio sam da se gresi koje počiniš uvek vraćaju da te progone
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.15,0:29:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}i da ću morati uvek da ih nosim sa sobom i prihvatim sve kazne koje me snađu.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.86,0:29:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tako...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.47,0:29:49.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kreten
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.65,0:29:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ostao sam sasvim sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.18,0:30:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.49,0:30:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevedite ovo za sledeći čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.19,0:30:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.24,0:30:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.27,0:30:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.14,0:30:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li predao svoj domaći iz matematike?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.98,0:30:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A, izvini. Zaboravio sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.97,0:30:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.24,0:30:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, onda bolje požuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.12,0:30:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoću, izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.34,0:30:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.52,0:31:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo u dvorište?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.16,0:31:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Išida je tako uvek sam, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.21,0:31:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poznat je po tome. Svi znaju za to."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.19,0:31:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljno?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.65,0:31:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A, opet gleda ovamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.72,0:31:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zar nije usamljen tako, uvek sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.61,0:31:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoće li tako provesti ceo život?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.76,0:31:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zašto li uopšte živi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.59,0:31:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.91,0:31:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kupio sam ovo na dan izlaska.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.72,0:31:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Mislim da ću da prestanem da budem fan onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.03,0:31:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.08,0:31:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa da.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.05,0:31:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljno?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.92,0:32:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ta frizura mi deluje poznato.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.95,0:32:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ko to beše?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.07,0:32:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nego...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.60,0:32:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smem li uopšte opet da vidim Nišimiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.88,0:32:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rekla je da često hrani šarane hlebom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.38,0:32:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali kako ja da joj izađem pred lice?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.98,0:32:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možda da se izvinim što sam je rasplakao?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rekla je da je tamo utorkom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.19,0:32:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Da li bih joj smetao?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.82,0:32:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Vratih se.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.32,0:33:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.96,0:33:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadi me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.13,0:33:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.43,0:33:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini za ono jutros.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.01,0:33:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Što sam spalila novac za koji si tako vredno radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.89,0:33:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali znaš, ne bih ni želela da koristim novac koji si zaradio sa ciljem da umreš.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.56,0:33:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.55,0:33:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaradiću ga ponovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A, hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.00,0:33:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da žuriš.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.19,0:33:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, sigurno si gladan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.82,0:33:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da jedemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.76,0:33:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladna!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.37,0:33:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Utorak...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.63,0:34:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, možeš li da mi pozajmiš svoj bicikl?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.81,0:34:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.88,0:34:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.87,0:34:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A, to je onaj lik.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.89,0:34:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nešto sam zaboravio.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.71,0:34:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem da ga pokupim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.10,0:34:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Zašto sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.14,0:34:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Koristi svoj bicikl.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.07,0:34:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitam te zato što nemam svoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.97,0:34:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.93,0:34:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.08,0:34:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, prekini.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.76,0:34:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Neka mi neko pomogne!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ej...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.31,0:34:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomozite mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.85,0:34:28.29,Alt,,0,0,0,,Do vraga!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.56,0:34:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.51,0:34:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomozite mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.83,0:34:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiri se, bre!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.83,0:34:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti to!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.86,0:34:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.52,0:34:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Možeš da uzmeš moj.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.49,0:34:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.53,0:34:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji si car.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.83,0:34:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nije mi ga vratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.01,0:34:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I baš danas na utorak.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.78,0:34:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možda je to neki znak - da ne idem?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.07,0:35:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nije da ne mogu i peške da odem,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.72,0:35:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ali kao da mi nešto govori "Ne idi!".
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.60,0:35:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nedostaje mi neki izgovor...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.45,0:35:08.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pufnasti novi hleb\NKupon za popust
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.67,0:35:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Treba mi neki fini, skroz prirodni razlog da odem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.20,0:35:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kupon za popust na pufnasti hleb?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.25,0:35:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To je to!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.91,0:35:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da li je Nišimija možda tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.35,0:35:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.39,0:35:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, tamo je.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.48,0:35:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.90,0:35:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija Šoko nije ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.23,0:35:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ali,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.83,0:35:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,jesi li ti stvarno njen prijatelj?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.71,0:35:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Doviđenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.63,0:35:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije ništa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.47,0:35:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Istrčao je neki miš.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.94,0:35:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neki skroz ljigavi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.83,0:36:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne brini. Neće se vraćati.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.02,0:36:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.37,0:36:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.43,0:36:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.94,0:36:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tu si!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.71,0:36:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.60,0:36:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidi ovo!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.79,0:36:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je tvoj bicikl, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.07,0:36:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobar tajming!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.56,0:36:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što je pisala tvoja adresa na njemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.34,0:36:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde si ga našao?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.59,0:36:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bio je odbačen u polju pirinča.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.85,0:36:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, baš sam ga tražio.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.49,0:37:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što sam uspeo da ti ga vratim.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.94,0:37:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.84,0:37:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.82,0:37:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako se beše zoveš?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.34,0:37:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.24,0:37:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedim iza tebe, znaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.85,0:37:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako je. Ovo je dobar hleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.88,0:37:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš malo, Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.07,0:37:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.58,0:37:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.21,0:37:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.83,0:37:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.24,0:37:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.07,0:37:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo negde posle škole.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.26,0:37:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto smo sad prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.06,0:37:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovamo, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.43,0:38:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo, Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.02,0:38:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Ništa.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.34,0:38:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, "Jašo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.78,0:38:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kao da smo "veliki" prijatelji, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.75,0:38:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I? Nešto te muči?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.15,0:38:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Slobodno možeš da mi ispričaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.82,0:38:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi smo najbolji prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.83,0:38:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci, Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.63,0:38:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta su uopšte prijatelji?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.10,0:38:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tipa, postoji li nešto što moraš da ispuniš da bi imao prava da budeš nekome prijatelj?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.21,0:38:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gle, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.30,0:38:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ispruži ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.23,0:39:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To su prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.53,0:39:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidiš, Išida,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.88,0:39:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ja mislim da prijateljstvo prkosi logici i rečima.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.32,0:39:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakva prava, kakvi bakrači?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.77,0:39:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupost.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.75,0:39:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.47,0:39:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ali tu je.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.56,0:39:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.00,0:39:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, ti si—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.51,0:39:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam njen dečko.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.43,0:39:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A, joj, pade.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.81,0:39:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim hleb, ne ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.97,0:39:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, ko bi rekao...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.35,0:39:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija voli mlađe momke?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.48,0:39:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, to je nekako neočekivano.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.31,0:39:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ovaj, uzmi bar ovaj hleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.55,0:39:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobar je.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.35,0:39:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.45,0:39:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako si došao ovde samo da bi se bolje osećao, odlazi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.35,0:39:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li to sve?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.71,0:40:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Doviđenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.71,0:40:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.20,0:40:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Moj ortak ti kaže da želi da vidi Nišimiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.35,0:40:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.17,0:40:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne smaraj i zovi je ovamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.56,0:40:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Otkud ti ovde, Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.74,0:40:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pratio sam te.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.75,0:40:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Najbolji smo prijatelji, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I za bednike važi - sličan se sa sličnim druži.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.22,0:40:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seronja.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.76,0:40:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim? Šta je tvoj problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.90,0:40:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Usudi se da to kažeš opet!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.65,0:40:28.31,Alt,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.04,0:40:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seronja!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.99,0:40:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidi ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.08,0:40:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta se dešava?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.63,0:40:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to Juzuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.93,0:40:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pobogu.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.74,0:40:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Svađaju se.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.15,0:40:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.81,0:40:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.46,0:40:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da stanemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.46,0:40:40.95,Alt,,0,0,0,,Povuci to!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.95,0:40:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.22,0:40:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više. Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.67,0:40:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.83,0:40:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bre, ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.17,0:40:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A, zar ti nisi onaj od pre neki dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.32,0:40:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, pomešali ste me...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.28,0:40:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Nagacuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.42,0:40:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.29,0:41:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do vraga!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.14,0:41:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Prokletstvo, sreli su se.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.95,0:41:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Svaka čast, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.95,0:41:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.13,0:41:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameravaš da ih špijuniraš?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.40,0:41:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj i meni da vidim!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.26,0:41:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.38,0:41:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida nekako čudno maše rukama.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.38,0:41:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To je znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.87,0:41:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.39,0:41:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Strava.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.95,0:41:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam znao da to ume.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.18,0:41:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, i ti znaš znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.89,0:41:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevedi mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.65,0:41:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ko je onaj seronja od malopre?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.77,0:41:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Neki skroz mi nepoznati lik."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.57,0:41:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Baš je odvratan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.43,0:41:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevedi lepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.70,0:41:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.76,0:41:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da padneš, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.47,0:41:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Da budem iskren, mislio sam da je bolje da ne dolazim pred tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.47,0:42:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Proveo sam prethodne dve nedelje razmišljajući o smislu prijateljstva.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.05,0:42:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tražio sam razlog da se ponovo vidimo."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.85,0:42:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.36,0:42:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Drago mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.05,0:42:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja sam razmišljala o tome.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.48,0:42:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Smešno je, zar ne?"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.57,0:42:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.20,0:42:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvoli, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.50,0:42:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hleb. Za šarane.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.95,0:42:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Voliš da ih hraniš?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.87,0:42:51.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore\NNišimija Šoko, odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.30,0:43:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, verovatno je bolje da ipak ne gledaš unutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.28,0:43:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.62,0:43:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uskočila je...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.34,0:43:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.28,0:43:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li se nešto desilo Išidi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.61,0:43:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.36,0:43:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida je skočio u reku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.63,0:43:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.63,0:43:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.69,0:43:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta radiš, bre?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.49,0:43:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.39,0:43:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.62,0:44:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.29,0:44:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ispala mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.57,0:44:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Šoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.61,0:44:46.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sme li iko da mi izađe na crtu?\NIšida Šoja
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.06,0:44:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto ti, na.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.58,0:44:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li videla ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.66,0:44:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta, bre? Zar to nije Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.35,0:44:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Vidimo se ponovo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.21,0:45:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno joj ne smeta?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.84,0:45:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.73,0:45:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo si ti, Išida, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.98,0:45:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.37,0:45:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Š-Šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.99,0:45:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, pođi sa mnom do zbornice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.32,0:45:24.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,Suspenzija od nedelju dana - Išida Šoja
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.37,0:45:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Skočio sam sa mosta Suimon u reku uprkos tome što je to zabranjeno,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.91,0:45:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,i zatim sam tu sliku okačio na internet..."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.15,0:45:33.95,Alt,,0,0,0,,Šoja!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.07,0:45:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ali možeš li da odeš da pokupiš Mariju?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.30,0:45:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne smem da izlazim dok sam suspendovan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.01,0:45:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde, malo, šta fali?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.15,0:45:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala unapred.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.24,0:45:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.55,0:45:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, bre...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.15,0:46:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Vreme je da idemo kući, Marija.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.66,0:46:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.37,0:46:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Neko je unutra!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.58,0:46:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.13,0:46:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.19,0:46:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.79,0:46:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nisi ti Nišimijin dečko?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.20,0:46:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Prehladićeš se.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.17,0:46:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa to je onaj miš.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.99,0:46:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta radiš na ovakvom mestu?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.31,0:46:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde ti je obuća?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.92,0:46:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne ljutiš se?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.90,0:46:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zbog čega?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.74,0:46:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam okačio onu tvoju sliku na internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.31,0:46:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A, to si bio ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.38,0:46:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, koliko mi je laknulo što si to bio ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.16,0:47:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta pričaš to?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.66,0:47:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim, nekako mi je jasno zašto si to uradio.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.22,0:47:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Naljuti se na mene onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.64,0:47:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, ne mogu.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.50,0:47:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To sam zaslužio.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.77,0:47:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.00,0:47:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladna sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.48,0:47:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dolazim.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.95,0:47:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Odoh onda ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.95,0:47:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti piči kući što pre.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.40,0:47:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoje dete?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.77,0:47:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.34,0:47:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sestrino!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.56,0:47:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.98,0:47:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.20,0:47:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jedi koliko voliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.47,0:47:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde je sestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.02,0:47:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rekla je da će kasniti večeras.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.32,0:47:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Je l' ti nije vruće, Marija?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.10,0:47:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ukusno je!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.45,0:47:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Super.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.12,0:47:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru, ne jedeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.35,0:48:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.38,0:48:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci "a"!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.59,0:48:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.18,0:48:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do vraga...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.83,0:48:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.13,0:49:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadih se kad si nestao.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.71,0:49:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo, kišobran.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.34,0:49:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma samo ga uzmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.62,0:49:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljan sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.52,0:49:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.26,0:49:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nego...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.04,0:49:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako sam i mislio.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.51,0:49:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš ove?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.03,0:49:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Moje su, ali ih više ne nosim.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.01,0:49:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Daću ti ih.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.63,0:49:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si pobegao od kuće?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.41,0:49:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Posvađao sam se sa Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.94,0:49:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.01,0:49:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači ono, kao, problemi u vašoj vezi, i tako to?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.23,0:49:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Koristio sam njen šampon a da je nisam pitao.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.37,0:49:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oterala me je iz kuće.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.75,0:49:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, vi živite zajedno?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.31,0:49:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drži kišobran nad sobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.62,0:49:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Imamo samo jedan, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.08,0:50:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, ja sam kriv što nisam poneo dva.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.68,0:50:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A i ako se prehladiš, kako ću da izađem Nišimiji pred oči?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.98,0:50:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.84,0:50:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Koja je fora sa tim licemerjem?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.73,0:50:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokupiš lutalicu sa ulice da bi se bolje osećao?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.47,0:50:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo ti je zanimljivo...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.97,0:50:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maltretirao si je zato što ne čuje, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.25,0:50:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A sada si našao da naučiš znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.76,0:50:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Čemu sad to?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.59,0:50:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš da si sad postao dobra osoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.45,0:50:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Odvratan si.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.68,0:50:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.38,0:50:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa da, čuo si od Nišimije.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.67,0:50:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, tako je.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.33,0:50:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam odvratno ljudsko biće.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.03,0:50:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Zapravo nemam prava da živim.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.71,0:51:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali poželeo sam da barem Nišimija više ne plače.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.83,0:51:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A, naravno, ne nameravam da se mešam među vas dvoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.80,0:51:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To se neće desiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.70,0:51:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ovo sve moram i zbog sebe da uradim...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.89,0:51:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.84,0:51:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.25,0:51:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako je.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.26,0:51:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini što ti sad rušim iluzije,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.17,0:51:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,ali ja sam Šokoina...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.95,0:51:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.77,0:51:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mlađa sestra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.59,0:51:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.75,0:52:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimijina majka...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.34,0:52:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.14,0:52:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, to boli.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.21,0:52:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.86,0:52:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vratila sam se.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.18,0:52:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Juduru!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.22,0:52:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seko?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.91,0:52:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Idvini! Idvini!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.15,0:52:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I meni je žao.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.64,0:52:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pije mi se bakin sok od perile.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.95,0:52:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru, bolje da se držiš podalje od onog dečaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.77,0:52:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci to i Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.46,0:52:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To ćemo same odlučiti,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.09,0:52:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,i ja i seka.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.79,0:52:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.43,0:52:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ima?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.07,0:52:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si danas došao?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.67,0:52:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vratim pozajmljeni kišobran.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.72,0:52:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,O, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.07,0:53:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Prilično si odgovoran.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.12,0:53:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka, to nije "momak".
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.61,0:53:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To je Nišimijina mlađa sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.19,0:53:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, skapirao sam od ranije.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.97,0:53:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što si prijateljica mom Jašou.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.64,0:53:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je moj prijatelj Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.73,0:53:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.48,0:53:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,kupio sam mobilni.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.96,0:53:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, i ti ga imaš, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.92,0:53:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da li razmenjuješ poruke sa prijateljima?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.89,0:53:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz srednje?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.12,0:53:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To je baš fino.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.47,0:53:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima li još neko sa kime bi želela da razmenjuješ poruke?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.22,0:53:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Neko čiji bi broj želela da znaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.58,0:53:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa da. Mogao bih da ti kažem moj...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.20,0:53:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.61,0:53:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa... ha... ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.01,0:54:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sahara, iz osnovne škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.17,0:54:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.37,0:54:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.47,0:54:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li ići da nađeš tu Saharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.69,0:54:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa hajde, nije tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.27,0:54:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali mislim da si ti baš odgovorna.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.83,0:54:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.54,0:54:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.49,0:54:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, Mašiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.92,0:54:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.24,0:54:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.52,0:54:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Želeo bih nešto da te pitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.96,0:54:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li možda imaš kontakt informacije od Sahare, iz osnovne škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.60,0:54:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sahare?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.39,0:54:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, nemam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.35,0:54:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali znam u koju školu ide.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.06,0:54:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao ide u istu.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.23,0:54:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ženska akademija Taijo".
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.91,0:54:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do vraga. Švorc sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.64,0:54:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, uzmi ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.72,0:55:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta, bre? Ne treba mi toliko.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.63,0:55:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne brini o tome, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.79,0:55:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trebaće ti za put, hranu, i hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.08,0:55:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Biće ti lakše ako budeš imao bar ovoliko.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.33,0:55:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.99,0:55:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.55,0:55:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dovela sam je.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.99,0:55:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seka se naljutila što je izostavljaš iako je ovo bila njena ideja.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.22,0:55:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ali moraćeš da je povedeš, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.40,0:55:51.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,Jesi li umoran?\NJuzuru mi je dala tvoj broj.\NHvala ti na ovome.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.91,0:56:01.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Bila sam jako srećna kada sam čula da si našao Saharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.00,0:56:05.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Juzuru mi je ispričala puno o tebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.96,0:56:07.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti još jednom na ovome!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.06,0:56:20.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ženska akademija Taijo
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.25,0:56:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vidimo... Odavde idemo peške...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.66,0:56:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.31,0:56:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.07,0:56:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.56,0:56:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To sam ja, Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.55,0:56:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sećaš li me se?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.83,0:56:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.71,0:56:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.87,0:56:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Davno se nismo videle, je l' tako?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.79,0:56:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Od onda sam nastavila da učim znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.79,0:57:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li sam to dobro pokazala?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.54,0:57:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini što sam...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.63,0:57:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,iznenada nestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.48,0:57:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Od onda sam se uvek pitala šta je bilo sa tobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.01,0:57:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što smo se ponovo videle.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.79,0:57:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadila sam se.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.55,0:57:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.87,0:57:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, da.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.98,0:57:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,U koju školu ti ideš?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.21,0:57:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.27,0:57:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, tvoje grudi su porasle.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.58,0:57:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji broj nosiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.90,0:57:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj da proverim!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.57,0:57:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.72,0:57:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Moram do toaleta.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.47,0:57:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha, u redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.93,0:57:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Delimo kupone za popust!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.03,0:58:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.92,0:58:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Delimo kupone za popust!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.95,0:58:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.48,0:58:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Delimo kupone za popust!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.55,0:58:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.83,0:58:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Posetite nas!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.89,0:58:24.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,Klub "Mjau mjau"
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.39,0:58:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Klub "Mjau mjau"?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.44,0:58:37.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sahara:\NSvaka čast, Išida, naučio si znakovni jezik?\NTakođe - hvala ti što si nas opet povezao!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Svaka čast Sahari.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.65,0:58:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ne bih mogao ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.28,0:58:44.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,Snimi video zapis
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.58,0:58:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Da nastavim ovako i povežem Nišimiju sa Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.90,0:58:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Nema šanse.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.75,0:58:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, i ja tako mislim.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.64,0:59:02.89,Signs,,0,0,0,,Klub "Mjau mjau"
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.30,0:59:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.53,0:59:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo li da uđemo, Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.42,0:59:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Napred, u klub "Mjau mjau"!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.14,0:59:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrodo—
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.94,0:59:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrodošli!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.67,0:59:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Koliko želite da ostanete?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.73,0:59:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jedan sat, molim.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.41,0:59:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Imamo kupon za popust.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.51,0:59:17.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljno?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.35,0:59:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Naravno. Hvala vam.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.09,0:59:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne verujem, stvarno je došao.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.95,0:59:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš, nekako...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.65,0:59:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta li si ti očekivao?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.19,0:59:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I ti isto?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.92,0:59:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne pričaj gluposti.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.26,0:59:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Došao sam vođen iskrenom željom da nađemo tvoju prijateljicu.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.88,0:59:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je. Tvoju prijateljicu...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.43,0:59:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li ona ovde?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.08,0:59:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo baš prijatelji, doduše...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.03,0:59:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.30,0:59:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta toga se desilo u šestom osnovne.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.15,0:59:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo se baš najprijatnije rastali.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.34,0:59:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne vidim je.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.87,1:00:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo li nazad, onda?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.95,1:00:07.37,Signs,,0,0,0,,Soba za testiranje sluha
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.11,1:00:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Buba!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.14,1:00:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A, došla si?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.24,1:00:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Došla sam da se igram sa Marijom.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.47,1:00:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš li da bi se ovo svidelo Nišimiji?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.07,1:00:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maca!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.31,1:00:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulazim, seko!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.21,1:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seko?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.50,1:00:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Poklon; staviću ga ovde.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.90,1:01:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,U...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.77,1:01:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.87,1:01:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.01,1:01:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.45,1:01:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Davno se nismo videli.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.52,1:01:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.21,1:01:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Istina.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.85,1:01:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.77,1:01:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.15,1:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I dalje sama, vidim.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.71,1:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jadnica.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.66,1:01:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali stvarno, Išida, stvarno se nismo davno videli.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.22,1:01:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde neki put da se družimo.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.99,1:01:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Neka, hvala.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.91,1:01:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrziš me, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.52,1:01:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa ne baš.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.87,1:01:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uvek sam mislila kako sam trebala da ti pomognem nekako.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.48,1:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, za osnovnu.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.53,1:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Ueno. Siđi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.41,1:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to torbica sa mog posla?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.91,1:02:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je ima? Užas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.83,1:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam joj je dao.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.43,1:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A, stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.34,1:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.61,1:02:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.50,1:02:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.86,1:02:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Davno se nismo videle, Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.26,1:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.38,1:02:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hej!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.94,1:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Nosiš samo jedan?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.19,1:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.55,1:02:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabavićemo se tako što ćemo ga baciti. Baš kao nekada.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.08,1:02:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.69,1:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.85,1:02:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zavitlavaš se, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.42,1:02:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stani malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.85,1:02:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vas dvoje možda ne izlazite?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.98,1:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Naravno da ne.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.07,1:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji smo.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.46,1:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji? Kakva šala!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.78,1:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelj a maltretirao si je?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.87,1:03:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.90,1:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne vredi, ovo je presmešno.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.55,1:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zbog osećaja krivice?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.81,1:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.14,1:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, stvarno si postao jadan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.66,1:03:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, želim vam da se zabavite igrajući se prijatelja.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.78,1:03:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta smo pričali?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.32,1:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ništa posebno.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.34,1:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem onda ja.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.23,1:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.74,1:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Juduru.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.73,1:04:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.29,1:04:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Juto je.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.49,1:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Budna sam. Od iznenađenja.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.23,1:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jedi douča—
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.58,1:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, ček... Pre toga...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.05,1:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.29,1:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Seko...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.36,1:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Danas imaš repić.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.39,1:04:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto...?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.75,1:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakvo čudno lice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.79,1:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Moram da pokažem Išidi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.76,1:04:40.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Juzuru:\NGomila šarana danas.\NTreba neko da ih hrani. Dođi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.82,1:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimi—
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.55,1:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Vezala je kosu u rep?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.73,1:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, ge ideš?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.78,1:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde idem?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.99,1:05:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do pekare.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.62,1:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru me je zamolila da kupim hleb za šarane.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.81,1:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Imamo dooljno. Juduru je šamo alaba.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.63,1:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.11,1:05:28.01,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ne molaš da kupi—
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.01,1:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj. Koristi znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.19,1:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li dvučim šudno?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.03,1:05:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.42,1:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.29,1:05:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Skroz je u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.90,1:05:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Moram da odem da kupim hleb.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.27,1:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.06,1:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.48,1:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Za mene?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.05,1:06:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.09,1:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogu li da pogledam?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.94,1:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je, bre, ovo?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.20,1:06:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.89,1:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...izađ.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.07,1:06:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.79,1:06:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ove?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.82,1:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...izađ.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.47,1:06:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Izađ sadmno!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.84,1:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Izašao... Mesec?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.01,1:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.18,1:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš je lep večeras.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.51,1:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.63,1:07:18.59,Signs,,0,0,0,,Slobodan? Hajmo na film!\NTvoj "veliki" prijatelj, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.88,1:07:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.73,1:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li te ovo podseća na Mesec?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.64,1:07:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Na Mesec? Ne baš, ne.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.31,1:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Možd—
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.58,1:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Deluje da nisu slatkiši.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.19,1:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija mi je ih dala malopre.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.10,1:07:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno, šta li je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.34,1:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta se desilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.75,1:07:50.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pitala sam Išidu da izađe sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.21,1:07:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.63,1:07:55.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ali nije me skapirao.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.80,1:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A, promenila si frizuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.06,1:08:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si je promenila?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.41,1:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Da se nije nešto desilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.88,1:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš ti dobro stoji!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.63,1:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.05,1:08:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Samo sam žurila jutros.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.86,1:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno? Ali baš ti lepo stoji.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.48,1:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, Kavai...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.65,1:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si promenila frizuru?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.83,1:08:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto, pitaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.41,1:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bez nekog posebnog razloga.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.33,1:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Takve su ti devojke.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.60,1:08:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.16,1:08:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.02,1:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pre neki dan je Mašiba rekao da bi želeo da bude tvoj prijatelj.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.32,1:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si ti ovde?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.68,1:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je. Ja sam Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.99,1:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zdravo. Ja sam Mašiba.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.71,1:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stoj, bre!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.60,1:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde ćete mi preko glave?!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.23,1:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je da te vidim, Mijo!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.78,1:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, gde je Nišimija danas?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.85,1:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kući, rekla je da je boli stomak.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.87,1:09:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Da me ne izbegava?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.58,1:09:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.46,1:09:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pre neki dan je pokušavala nešto da mi saopšti, ali nisam mogao da je razumem.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.94,1:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je rekla?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.57,1:09:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Da je izašao... Mesec.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.30,1:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jednostavne reči, ali nisam razumeo njihov smisao.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.76,1:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, da, ne čudi me da se iznervirala.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.57,1:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, ako se brineš da te ne izbegava, zašto je ne pozoveš?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.03,1:09:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne bude htela da izađe, reći će tako.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.87,1:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.03,1:09:45.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hej... Nekoliko nas planira izlazak, hoćeš sa nama?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.13,1:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde prvo da stanemo u red ovamo!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.66,1:10:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Držite se blizu mene!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.74,1:10:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je ona preuzela kontrolu?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.85,1:10:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemam pojma.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.19,1:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.22,1:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa njom?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.10,1:10:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponaša se previše prijateljski.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.94,1:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno? Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.50,1:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Neko poznat Šoko?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.26,1:10:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.93,1:10:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz osnovne.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.31,1:10:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Je l' slobodno tu, Sahara?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.20,1:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha. Izvoli.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.11,1:10:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomalo je strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.03,1:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeste li svi spremni?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.13,1:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesmo!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.95,1:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Krenimo onda!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.74,1:10:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Da ti možda ne smeta što je Ueno tu?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.66,1:10:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ne.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.83,1:10:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pohađamo isti smer u našoj školi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.26,1:10:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Naučila sam puno od nje.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.62,1:11:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,U osnovnoj sam se plašila da se vozim rolerkosterom.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.98,1:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bila sam plašljivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.94,1:11:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali pokušala sam da promenim perspektivu.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.24,1:11:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rešila sam da neću odlučiti da li je strašno dok ne probam.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.84,1:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada ipak jeste strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.71,1:11:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto ga.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.15,1:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, pazi, pazi!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.70,1:11:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Noge ti klecaju, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.11,1:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.49,1:11:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Strava.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.12,1:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.79,1:12:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mora da si se baš trudio, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.66,1:12:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej! Šta je sa ovom rukom?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.75,1:12:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Vređaš mog Jašoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.83,1:12:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Samo sam druželjubiv.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.26,1:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Neće moći! Ne tako lako!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.18,1:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš si blesav, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.79,1:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko želi da priđe Jašou mora da dobije moju dozvolu!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.77,1:12:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li tvoja kosa prirodna?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.19,1:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.87,1:12:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne diraj me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.96,1:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.62,1:12:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Beži, Mašiba!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.91,1:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, Jašo, stignimo ih!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.15,1:12:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.63,1:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imam li ja prava da se ovoliko zabavljam?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.42,1:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ovo je nekako kao...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.91,1:12:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.45,1:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onako, kao da smo prijatelji!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.83,1:12:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.96,1:13:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jede mi se takojaki.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.46,1:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da ga kupimo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.68,1:13:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Ček.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.67,1:13:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Vaš takojaki.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.51,1:13:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.53,1:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj, Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.19,1:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo stvarno nije bilo potrebno.
Comment: 0,1:13:22.83,1:13:23.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,Umri, izdajice!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.66,1:13:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Š-Šimada?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.34,1:13:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.74,1:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, javiću ti se!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.53,1:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.50,1:13:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ljut?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.97,1:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.06,1:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam ljut.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.11,1:13:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Samo sam se nadala da biste mogli opet da se družite kao nekad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.87,1:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislila sam da ćete naći zajednički jezik.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.03,1:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko ti to nije tražio.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.90,1:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.61,1:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam li i ja uradio istu stvar?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.92,1:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti i ja smo slični.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.32,1:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.80,1:14:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesmo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.41,1:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.64,1:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.79,1:14:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Svi bi bili srećni kada ne bi bilo Nišimije, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.99,1:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko si ti da to odlučiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.47,1:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali jednostavno je tako.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.69,1:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Da nje nije bilo, ne bi bilo problema između mene i Sahare.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.61,1:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A ti i Šimada biste ostali prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.67,1:14:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da sve bude kao nekad, pre nego što je ona došla.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.92,1:14:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Za to sa mnom i Šimadom...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.73,1:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam tako presekao i to je to.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.63,1:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, da li ti mene mrziš?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.69,1:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Verovatno.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.60,1:15:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim da želim da se vozim na vrtešci.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.35,1:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ići ću sa Nišimijom.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.00,1:15:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.22,1:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, vozi se sa mnom na vrtešci.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.36,1:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.78,1:15:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponesi ovo, seko.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.82,1:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću još jedan krug na rolerkosteru.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.11,1:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A, zdravo, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.73,1:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoja je gore.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.89,1:15:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.84,1:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Imam strogo poverljivi snimak.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.99,1:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Snimak sa vrteške?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.95,1:15:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.11,1:15:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Kako?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.27,1:15:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostavila sam da snima.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.75,1:16:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.24,1:16:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja tebe mrzim.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.11,1:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostavi to.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.71,1:16:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pričaću sporo tako da možeš da razumeš
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.53,1:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,i slušaću pažljivo kada ti govoriš.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.66,1:16:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,U osnovnoj školi,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.09,1:16:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,ja nisam imala razumevanja za tebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.93,1:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ni ti nisi ni pokušala da razumeš mene, takođe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.19,1:16:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato si mi gurkala tvoju glupu svesku pod nos svaki čas
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.98,1:16:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,i uvek se blentavo smeškala.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.42,1:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A svaki put kada bi se nešto desilo, odmah si se izvinjavala.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.59,1:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato sam bila promenila svoj pristup.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.94,1:16:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorisala sam te, i ogovarala iza leđa.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.88,1:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To su bili znaci da mi se više ne približavaš.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.29,1:16:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali umesto da shvatiš te znake, ti si uzvratila.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.90,1:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Plačući si nas ocinkarila.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.71,1:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zbog toga je Išida izgubio sve prijatelje.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.29,1:17:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve oko nas se raspalo.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.28,1:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Idvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.93,1:17:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne želim da mi se izvinjavaš.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.53,1:17:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Obe smo radile šta smo morale,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.02,1:17:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,i sad kad pogledam, možda i nije moglo drugačije.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.49,1:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali nemam nameru da ti sada budem prijateljica.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.39,1:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I dalje te mrzim,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.07,1:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,i ti mrziš mene.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.75,1:17:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa zato šta kažeš da se ne forsiramo više?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.39,1:17:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukujmo se kao dvoje ljudi koji se jednostavno mrze.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.11,1:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Grežiš.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.81,1:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja mržim šebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.92,1:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta, bre?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.11,1:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ti to znači?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.53,1:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I šta onda?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.66,1:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li opet da mi se izviniš?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.40,1:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Na kraju je sve isto kao pre pet godina.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.65,1:18:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nećeš ni da pričaš sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.37,1:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta misliš?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.00,1:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj... da...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.71,1:18:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da Nišimija zavoli sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.49,1:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno, beše?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.52,1:18:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, šta sa njom?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.91,1:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li se nešto desilo između nje i Nišimije?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.18,1:18:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Zašto pitaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.90,1:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai je rekla da se svašta izdešavalo u osnovnoj školi.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.04,1:18:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija stvarno ne čuje, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.41,1:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.34,1:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, da nije zato maltretirana?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.45,1:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ne podnosim takve stvari.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.79,1:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar se ne slažeš, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.37,1:19:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Kako to misliš?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.44,1:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš da kažeš da ja tu širim neke priče o prošlosti?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.47,1:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Ček, glasna si.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.62,1:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uopšte se nisi promenio.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.30,1:19:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostao si užasan kao i u osnovnoj.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.42,1:19:21.84,Alt,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo, Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.84,1:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiri se, Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.77,1:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,O čemu ste pričali?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.21,1:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mašiba, Išida je nekada maltretirao jednu devojčicu.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.03,1:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to pričaš, Kavai?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.66,1:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema šanse...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.04,1:19:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Istina je!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.08,1:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti si je ogovarala.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.64,1:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja nikada nisam ogovarala Nišimiju.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.39,1:19:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimiju?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.46,1:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je! Išida je maltretirao Nišimiju!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.49,1:19:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš, ja sam pokušala da ga zaustavim.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.85,1:20:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali on nije slušao.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.02,1:20:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo je strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.93,1:20:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.71,1:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li do—
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.09,1:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.08,1:20:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.13,1:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.05,1:20:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ja mrzim sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.19,1:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.23,1:20:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.01,1:21:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.50,1:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Ništa.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.52,1:21:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.40,1:21:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tu si, Išida!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.51,1:21:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Doneo sam tvoju torbu.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.69,1:21:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Poz.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.51,1:21:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.87,1:21:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam je pozvala.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.35,1:21:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini za ono ranije.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.95,1:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ionako je sve bila tvoja krivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.51,1:21:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ipak, Mašiba je rekao da bi trebalo da ti oprostim, ako se izviniš Nišimiji.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.91,1:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.85,1:21:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To je glupost.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.98,1:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi nemamo prava da kritikujemo Išidu u vezi sa time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.00,1:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mi"?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.59,1:21:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisi u pravu, Nao.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.26,1:21:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to nisam?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.99,1:21:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Za razliku od mene, ti si se trudila da je maltretiraš.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.07,1:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne trpaj me u isti koš.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.44,1:22:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.47,1:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.24,1:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.25,1:22:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uopšte nismo iste. Ti si se samo smejala i oponašala me!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.72,1:22:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Užasna si!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.88,1:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ti kažeš, Sahara?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.37,1:22:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.59,1:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao je i tebe stalno ogovarala, Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.02,1:22:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Govorila sam samo istinu!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.39,1:22:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci, Sahara, kako je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.59,1:22:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.19,1:22:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam se plašila vas obe nekada.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.17,1:22:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Na čijoj si ti strani?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.51,1:22:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ničijoj!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.23,1:22:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.08,1:22:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve je moja krivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.80,1:22:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrzim takvo razmišljanje.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.73,1:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.81,1:22:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj sve da odlučuješ u tuđe ime.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.99,1:22:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, ne moraš baš tako...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.65,1:22:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više, Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.22,1:23:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ionako ćeš samo opet da pobegneš i zažališ što si bila plašljiva.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.25,1:23:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tobom, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.24,1:23:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više, Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.05,1:23:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oduvek si samo brinula za sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.03,1:23:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.19,1:23:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam tvoj saveznik.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.96,1:23:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti me više, ni ne poznaješ me kako treba, kakav saveznik?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.38,1:23:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više, ja odlazim!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.96,1:23:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.75,1:23:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu je.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.16,1:23:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Meni ne smeta.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.85,1:23:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.23,1:23:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.72,1:23:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.63,1:23:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije trebalo da dođem.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.16,1:23:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, užasan si.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.43,1:23:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemaš veze sa ovime, ne mešaj se.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.49,1:23:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A mislio sam da smo postali prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.17,1:24:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.25,1:24:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sledeće nedelje počinje letnji raspust.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.63,1:24:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš da idemo negde...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.42,1:24:39.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nemam pojma.\NIzvini.\NSlušaš li me?!\NIzvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.83,1:24:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzu?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.12,1:24:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Vid će ti se iskvariti ako budeš čitala u mraku.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.21,1:24:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.10,1:25:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Još uvek se brineš za svoju sestru?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.35,1:25:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Baka se brine za tebe, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.66,1:25:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalno razmišljaš o sestri.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.48,1:25:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A sebe ostavljaš po strani.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.83,1:25:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa i ti si ista, bako.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.17,1:25:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne ideš u klub penzionera, već učiš znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.66,1:25:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja to radim za sebe, pa je u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.72,1:25:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Onda i ja to radim za sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.63,1:25:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li tako?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.25,1:25:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti si dobra devojčica.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.84,1:25:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.18,1:25:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama stalno viče na mene.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.04,1:25:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam ni u školu išla odavno.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.54,1:25:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Srce ti je čisto.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.72,1:25:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I Šoko se trudi.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.90,1:25:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Blagoslovena sam divnim unukama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.43,1:26:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzmi i zemičke.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.32,1:26:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoću.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.35,1:26:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bako...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.99,1:26:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija. Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.44,1:26:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Danas imam neki baš fini hleb.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.64,1:26:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj hleb...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.27,1:26:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobar je, nalik tebi.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.50,1:26:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I zato...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.10,1:26:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to pričam, pobogu?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.63,1:26:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.26,1:26:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar neće da dođe danas?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.25,1:26:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.83,1:27:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Da te opet ne boli stomak?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.04,1:27:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, to je čudno.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.94,1:27:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Juzu—
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.04,1:27:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ili da idem kući.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.93,1:27:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.19,1:27:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.25,1:27:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako si to obučena?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.80,1:27:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa u uniformu, prirodno.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.05,1:27:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako izgledam?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.62,1:27:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.65,1:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa za školu.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.33,1:27:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije sada letnji raspust?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.98,1:27:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci stvarno, šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.97,1:27:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ništa.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.66,1:27:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Recimo da sam se spremila za maskenbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.33,1:28:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seka. Moram da idem.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.04,1:28:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Otpratiću te. Gde ideš?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.56,1:28:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne moraš.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.14,1:28:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.07,1:28:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno nema potrebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.39,1:28:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Plakala si malopre, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.00,1:28:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.35,1:28:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema nikakve veze sa tobom.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.22,1:28:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima, ili bar tako želim da mislim.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.79,1:28:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.47,1:28:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato što se brinem za tebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.17,1:28:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj sad i ti da pričaš kao moja baka.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.26,1:28:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro onda, kako god.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.78,1:28:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.81,1:28:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ovde je dovoljno.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.75,1:28:45.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sahrana - Nišimija Ito
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.44,1:28:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.38,1:28:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Drži se, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.65,1:28:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.78,1:29:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ipak je strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.95,1:30:06.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija. Hoćemo negde sutra?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.94,1:31:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Strava!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.45,1:31:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da bacimo pogled.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.02,1:31:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.74,1:31:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oladih se.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.95,1:31:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto se izvinjavaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.87,1:31:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Naravno da ne!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.71,1:31:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta kažeš da smislimo i nešto za sutra?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.16,1:31:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Može, Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.71,1:31:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rekla je da ću biti nesrećan ako budem provodio vreme sa njom.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.43,1:31:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meni, onome ko je izazvao svu njenu nesreću.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.22,1:32:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da vidim more.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.67,1:32:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da volim ljude.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.17,1:32:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i čudovišta imaju srca...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.27,1:32:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne znam kako ću ikada sve ispraviti.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.18,1:32:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.20,1:32:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, danas je i Juzuru sa nama? Super!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.04,1:32:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo da gledamo film?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.67,1:32:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš zabavno!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.66,1:32:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.59,1:32:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dođoh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.19,1:32:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, ovo je najbolji raspust ikad!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.52,1:32:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne, Juzuru?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.62,1:32:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ja znam...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.52,1:32:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali stvarno, svaki dan je bio vrh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.19,1:32:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.43,1:32:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde ćemo sutra?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.17,1:32:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo i sutra negde.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.80,1:33:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne možemo sutra. Imamo planove.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.13,1:33:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.43,1:33:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li luda, seko?!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.19,1:33:08.43,Alt,,0,0,0,,Šta pravite?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.83,1:33:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li ovo u redu?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.43,1:33:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Smem li ja da budem ovde?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.64,1:33:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Imaš misiju da nam pomogneš da napravimo tortu za rođendan naše majke.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.36,1:33:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoće li to biti u redu?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.13,1:33:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Da ne dobijem opet šamar?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.90,1:33:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti šamar, možda te i ubije.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.63,1:33:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.11,1:33:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgleda odlično!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.21,1:33:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radite?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.58,1:33:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je on ovde, Šoko?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.61,1:33:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta pokušavaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.83,1:33:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Napolje.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.83,1:33:38.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hajde, hajde, mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.17,1:33:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta fali? Danas proslavljamo.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.88,1:33:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.20,1:33:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro ti stoji.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.71,1:33:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Njam!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.43,1:33:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgleda da si nekako ostao živ, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.37,1:33:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.67,1:33:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uspele smo, seko.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.57,1:34:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.65,1:34:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Poslala sam jednu tvoju fotografiju na regionalno takmičenje.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.21,1:34:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.80,1:34:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo je htela da probamo.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.47,1:34:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Ali to su sve neke uvrnute slike.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.45,1:34:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije baš tako.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.17,1:34:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Što mi tu spletkarite iza leđa?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.67,1:34:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.89,1:34:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sledećeg utorka će biti veliki vatromet, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.07,1:34:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A, neka, preskočiću.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.70,1:34:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.11,1:34:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li je ovde u redu?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.32,1:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.26,1:35:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A, idem da kupim jakisobu.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.10,1:35:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.39,1:35:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.10,1:35:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A, i hvala što ste me pozvale kući pre neki dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.18,1:35:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li vaša majka...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.36,1:35:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha. Da li je bila srećna?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.48,1:35:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam mogao da procenim po izrazu.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.03,1:35:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kada je tvoj rođendan?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.32,1:35:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedmi jun?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.69,1:35:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa već je prošao, znači!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.07,1:35:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači već imaš osamnaest, je li?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.25,1:36:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da proslavimo tvoj sledeći rođendan zajedno, okej?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.27,1:36:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajoj, rekao sam "zajedno"!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.25,1:36:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako znači?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.33,1:36:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.19,1:36:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.27,1:36:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali vatromet još nije završen.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.00,1:36:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Moraš da učiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.41,1:36:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A, u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.00,1:36:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Otpratiću te.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.71,1:36:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.17,1:37:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako dakle.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.30,1:37:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se onda.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.20,1:37:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.71,1:37:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde je seka?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.98,1:37:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.60,1:37:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Možeš li da mi doneseš foto-aparat?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.09,1:37:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.87,1:37:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji mrak.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.26,1:37:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.96,1:37:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulazim.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.58,1:37:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto ga.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.21,1:37:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li napunjen?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.36,1:37:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I odavde se vidi vatromet?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.42,1:37:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A, eto je.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.60,1:37:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.39,1:38:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.07,1:38:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Č-Čekaj malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.46,1:38:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.65,1:38:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.58,1:38:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.38,1:38:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.91,1:38:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoko!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.31,1:39:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.83,1:39:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto, Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.42,1:39:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, zgrabi ivicu!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.75,1:39:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bože.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.84,1:39:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Molim te daj mi još samo malo snage.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.86,1:39:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neću više bežati od stvari.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.49,1:39:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od sutra,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.27,1:39:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}gledaću ljude u lice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.27,1:39:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od sutra, slušaću njihove glasove.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.22,1:39:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od sutra, ispraviću stvari.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.18,1:39:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.08,1:39:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja sam joj bio zadao taj ožiljak.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.33,1:39:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jesam li joj se izvinio kako treba?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.86,1:39:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.31,1:39:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Izvini, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.67,1:39:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Da li se još uvek ljutiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.61,1:39:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čoveče, baš sam zeznuo.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.61,1:40:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trebao sam da te pitam šta misliš o meni.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.45,1:40:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nego, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.98,1:40:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vidiš, ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.65,1:40:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.91,1:40:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja sestra je ispekla palačinke.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.37,1:40:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Marija će da vidi vatromet!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.97,1:40:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hladno...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.27,1:40:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali toplo...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.64,1:40:54.35,Signs,,0,0,0,,Lokalna bolnica Sumion
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.84,1:41:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Teto!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.50,1:41:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Juzuru!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.18,1:41:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Konačno sam te našla.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.81,1:41:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,U radnji se niko nije javljao.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.14,1:41:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A ovde su rekli da su posete zabranjene.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.41,1:41:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sada je u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.40,1:41:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Od danas su ga premestili.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.73,1:41:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde sa mnom, da ga vidiš.{?}{zapravo obrnuto, da ti vidi lice, ali on je u komi, tako da...?}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.20,1:41:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Teto, Šoko je...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.02,1:41:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gospođo Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.98,1:41:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gospođo Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.72,1:41:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite, jako mi je žao.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.61,1:41:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet smo vam izazvali probleme.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.93,1:41:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Istinski se izvinjavam.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.48,1:41:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemojte, molim vas!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.07,1:41:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigurna sam da je moj sin ponovo uradio nešto vašoj Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.23,1:41:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,U suprotnom...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.99,1:41:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Teto, on je spasao moju glupu sestru.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.84,1:41:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam bila isuviše nepažljiva.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.83,1:41:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.27,1:42:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.43,1:42:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas, ustanite.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.79,1:42:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meni je samo drago da je Šoko u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.78,1:42:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.07,1:42:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.96,1:42:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je Išida morao da se povredi?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.13,1:42:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini da izigravaš neku tragičnu heroinu!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.82,1:42:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci nešto.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.70,1:42:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Toliko sam namučila ljude oko sebe, i to mi je jako teško palo,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.20,1:42:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,pa sam pokušala da se ubijem.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.51,1:42:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se.", je l' da?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.87,1:42:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Koliko si samo uobražena?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.20,1:42:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti si prokleta pošast, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.80,1:42:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Najviše mrzim takve kao što si ti,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.01,1:42:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,one koji ne mogu da sagledaju situaciju iz tuđe perspektive!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.76,1:42:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.97,1:42:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko si, bre, ti?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.14,1:42:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ti njena majka?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.18,1:42:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekinite...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.78,1:43:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta rađaš decu ako ne možeš da se staraš o njima!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.35,1:43:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radite?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.04,1:43:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.92,1:43:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.62,1:43:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.41,1:43:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radite?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.88,1:43:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ti Šoko?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.87,1:43:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvin...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.35,1:43:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.95,1:43:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.04,1:43:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.28,1:43:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.21,1:44:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.71,1:44:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nekada sam mislila da seka neće hteti da se ubije ako vidi ove slike.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.29,1:44:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je trebalo da učinim?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.18,1:45:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Neće da se otvore.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.39,1:45:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Drži ih zatvorenim!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.09,1:45:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nisam te video, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.60,1:45:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo negde da sednemo? Ja častim.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.07,1:45:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Čuo sam šta se desilo sa Jašom.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.00,1:45:26.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Uništila sam sve što je Išida izgradio.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.30,1:45:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš na ono što se desilo na mostu?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.87,1:45:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo je prihvatio čudaka kao što sam ja.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.40,1:45:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Učinio je da po prvi put shvatim šta je to najbolji prijatelj.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.55,1:45:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo je moj "veliki" prijatelj, i stvarno želim da se probudi.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.82,1:46:01.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,Želim da popravim ono što sam uništila.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.40,1:46:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar da ti padne na pamet da se ubiješ zato što ti je teško!?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.57,1:46:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai, preglasna si.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.98,1:46:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ona me neće čuti ako ne budem glasna.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.09,1:46:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako smo se brinuli!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.80,1:46:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Svi prolaze kroz neke poteškoće tokom života.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.68,1:46:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To važi za sve nas, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.97,1:46:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato moraš da naučiš da voliš i svoje loše osobine kako bi nastavila da koračaš napred.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.48,1:46:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je da si dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.74,1:46:44.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,Želim da popravim ono što sam uništila.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.72,1:46:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Razumem.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.00,1:46:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pričala si sa svima?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.64,1:46:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaka si.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.12,1:46:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja nemam toliko samopouzdanja.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.52,1:47:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne znam kako ću da se suočim sa Išidom kada se probudi.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.44,1:47:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja nisam uspela da se promenim.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.71,1:47:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet nisam uspela da te zaštitim!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.20,1:47:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I dalje sam plašljivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.49,1:47:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomeničeš še od šada,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.77,1:47:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahada...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.49,1:47:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti što si došla, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.62,1:48:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bre, prekini više.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.21,1:48:17.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.46,1:48:20.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,Našao sam te.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.18,1:48:24.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.35,1:48:26.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,Znaš,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.97,1:48:29.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,ovo je nekako čudno, ha?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.10,1:48:31.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.35,1:48:33.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,želeo sam da umrem...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.19,1:48:35.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,A.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.73,1:48:38.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,Još malo pa je prošao utorak.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.11,1:48:40.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.86,1:48:41.82,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.98,1:49:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.23,1:49:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.18,1:49:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.23,1:49:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Skidajte ovo sa mene!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.03,1:50:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.65,1:50:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.80,1:50:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.59,1:50:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.58,1:50:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.69,1:50:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.76,1:51:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.30,1:51:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je da si dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.13,1:51:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.52,1:51:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam sada dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.58,1:51:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Manje - više.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.19,1:51:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj tako da me gledaš, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.11,1:51:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.59,1:51:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.93,1:52:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.04,1:52:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam se stvarno izvinio za sve ono što sam ti učinio u prošlosti.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.76,1:52:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A ni za ono kasnije.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.55,1:52:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Verovatno sam u svojoj glavi stvorio sliku tebe kakva mi je odgovarala.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.96,1:52:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Želeo sam više da pričam sa tobom.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.79,1:52:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Verovatno je to bilo sve.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.90,1:52:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ja sam te povredio
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.37,1:52:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,i naterao da napraviš najgori mogući izbor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.72,1:52:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.10,1:52:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti ši pao žato što ja nišam mogla da se pomenim!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.21,1:52:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Šve je moja kvivica!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.69,1:53:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Da šamo mene nie bilo...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.09,1:53:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvini!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.03,1:53:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim te, ne plači, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.12,1:53:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.84,1:53:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pričao sam sa tobom do malopre.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.17,1:53:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo je to u snu.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.12,1:53:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgledalo je da sam odustao od svega.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.87,1:53:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali to nije bilo ispravno.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.96,1:53:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja sam ranije razmišljao slično kao ti,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.43,1:53:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ali sam ipak shvatio da ne zaslužujem da umrem.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.65,1:53:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da se izvinim i ostalima.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.67,1:53:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj, Nišimija. Ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.04,1:54:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja želim da mi pomogneš da živim.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.77,1:54:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.59,1:54:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Ha?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.92,1:54:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesam li ja upravo rekao nešto mnogo čudno?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.93,1:54:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajoj!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.42,1:54:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Izvini! Zaboravi to!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.67,1:54:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboravi to što sam sad rekao!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.85,1:55:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stigli smo na vaše odredište, {\i1}gospodine{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.62,1:55:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, Marija. Zalivaš cveće?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.93,1:55:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš si dobra devojčica.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.51,1:55:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li da umreš?!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.63,1:55:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Marija, Šo je oživeo.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.13,1:55:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam umro, Marija.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.15,1:55:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije li to Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.05,1:55:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ona se starala o tebi sve vreme.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.83,1:55:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Idi zahvali joj se.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.14,1:55:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Čujem da si dolazila da me posetiš.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.57,1:55:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam užasna osoba.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.44,1:55:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak ni u ovakvoj situaciji, nisam mogla da se zbližim sa Nišimijom.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.99,1:55:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada možda i nije bilo potrebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.43,1:56:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nego, oni koji su te izvukli iz vode kada si pao su bili Šimada i Hirose.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.64,1:56:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada rekli su mi da ti ne kažem.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.84,1:56:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.92,1:56:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrodošao nazad.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.72,1:56:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, odoh sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.10,1:56:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.68,1:56:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pobogu. Pa ovo je previše kratko!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.10,1:56:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo vam stoji mnogo bolje.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.82,1:56:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A, dobrodošao nazad, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.49,1:56:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se na smetnji.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.50,1:56:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dobar dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.52,1:56:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.51,1:56:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.08,1:56:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.47,1:56:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ne...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.76,1:56:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja se izvinjavam.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.94,1:56:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je. Moj sin je neuništiv.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.25,1:56:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Majka!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.19,1:56:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem da pokupim Mariju.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.98,1:56:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.06,1:56:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko je to?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.65,1:56:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moj zet. Vratio se.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.75,1:56:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.18,1:56:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru je gore.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.09,1:57:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj joj žele iz frižidera.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.13,1:57:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.40,1:57:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zimska uniforma?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.48,1:57:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro ti stoji.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.54,1:57:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidi ovo, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.04,1:57:11.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Fotografsko takmičenje - dobitnik učeničke nagrade\NNišimija Juzuru (3. razred niže srednje)
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.78,1:57:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš! Strava!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.18,1:57:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A vidi i ovo.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.38,1:57:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš? Strašno...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.36,1:57:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim te, šefe!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.78,1:57:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Podučavaj me!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.13,1:57:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.18,1:57:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Počela si da ideš u školu, znači?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.86,1:57:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoko me je motivisala.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.32,1:57:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, daću sve od sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.49,1:57:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Da ne izneverim nikoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.72,1:57:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Čujem sutra imaš školski festival?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.07,1:57:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, tako je.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.28,1:57:50.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nišimija: Dolazimo na festival sutra.\NČekaću pred kapijom u 10.\NJuzuru i mama će doći kasnije.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.83,1:57:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dobro jutro, narode.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.95,1:57:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako ste?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.62,1:57:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite za užasne stvari što sam rekao.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.99,1:58:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.23,1:58:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Odoh.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.23,1:58:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Čuvaj se.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.62,1:58:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Je l' se to tako koristi?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.31,1:58:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.22,1:58:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nema veze.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.36,1:58:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.80,1:58:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Srećno!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.75,1:58:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.09,1:58:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo li?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.81,1:58:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.77,1:58:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.00,1:58:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Onaj hospitalizovan?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.32,1:58:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Što je skočio?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.26,1:59:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam ti ovo rekao ranije,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.62,1:59:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,ali ja se ne uklapam najbolje u svoju školu.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.43,1:59:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne mogu da gledam ljude u lice.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.95,1:59:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato mi je lakše kada gledam dole, u pod.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.34,1:59:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogu da gledam dole?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.80,1:59:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.70,1:59:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogu da hodam i sam...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.98,1:59:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.91,1:59:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je moje odeljenje.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.42,1:59:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li voda spremna?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:40.00,1:59:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Još samo malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.19,1:59:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.23,1:59:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To je Išida!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.15,1:59:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ozdravio?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.93,1:59:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.30,1:59:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim da me je stomak malo zaboleo.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.11,1:59:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.28,1:59:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.39,2:00:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.01,2:00:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.77,2:00:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo, boli te stomak?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.72,2:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.13,2:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nagacuka. Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.45,2:00:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.87,2:00:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Što se tiče onoga—
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.42,2:00:28.56,Alt,,0,0,0,,Zašto gledaš na dole?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.56,2:00:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Baš čudno.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.31,2:00:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Zapravo sam hteo da te pogledam pravo u oči.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.92,2:00:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da se nisam uplašio?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.60,2:00:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.91,2:00:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.95,2:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako mi je drago što si dobro.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.67,2:00:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Da se nisi...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.93,2:00:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Da se nisi probudio, sa mnom bi bilo gotovo!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.96,2:00:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.92,2:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da brineš za ono što se desilo na mostu.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.38,2:01:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Takve stvari se dešavaju u životu.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.88,2:01:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato, molim te, Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.69,2:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne idi nigde!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.15,2:01:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim te!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.93,2:01:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.03,2:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, za sve.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.07,2:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.43,2:01:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.54,2:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A, i takođe...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.85,2:01:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tim brkovima?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.01,2:01:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To je bio deo molitve, da se probudiš što pre.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.69,2:01:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.60,2:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.67,2:01:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Čuo sam Nagacuku kako uzvikuje tvoje ime.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.47,2:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.03,2:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai, trebalo bi da ih daš Išidi.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.47,2:01:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Donela si ih?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.27,2:01:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Donela sam ih, ali ne mogu da mu ih dam. Nisu ispali dobro.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.00,2:01:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa šta fali? Hajde da mu damo.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.83,2:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.00,2:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zapravo sam želela da skupim hiljadu komada, ali nisam uspela.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.00,2:02:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zamolila sam sve, ali...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.23,2:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.65,2:02:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Ne, ovo je neverovatno!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.39,2:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je sasvim dovoljno!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.66,2:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikada nisam dobio ovako nešto,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.99,2:02:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,pa sam baš, stvarno, srećan.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.41,2:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti, Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.03,2:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I izvini.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.09,2:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti, Mašiba.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.72,2:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, tebi svaka čast.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.17,2:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Odvratno.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.36,2:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Igrate se prijatelja?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.09,2:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Koža mi se naježila.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.48,2:02:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto moraš da budeš takva?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.39,2:02:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.14,2:02:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tobom, Kavai? Hoćeš svađu sa mnom?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.62,2:02:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, hej, smirite se.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.79,2:02:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.48,2:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.66,2:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Toliko si se mučio, a nisam mogla da ti pomognem.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.35,2:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uopšte se nisam promenila.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.38,2:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj tako.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.28,2:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja sam isti.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.91,2:03:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne pričaju ni o čemu ozbiljnom.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.49,2:03:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet si se izvinila.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.27,2:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, takva si i šta je tu je.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.80,2:03:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupačo.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.07,2:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupačo.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.38,2:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupačo.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.09,2:03:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A, bre, zaboravi.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.90,2:03:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem da pojedem nešto.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.54,2:03:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pobegla je.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.62,2:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Postidela se.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.04,2:03:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušajte, želeo bih nešto da vas zamolim.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.95,2:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Smem li?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.48,2:03:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Želeo bih da svi zajedno prošetamo festivalom.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.97,2:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, ovo je baš ukusno!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.91,2:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde posle da pogledamo u salu.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.25,2:04:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro je smeo da dođe u školu.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.57,2:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, tezga odeljenja B je strava.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.23,2:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo.
